Your task: Complete visual/UX redesign of herostorybooks.com.

CRITICAL REQUIREMENTS:
1. Generate 3-4 real storybook illustration images via fal.ai API (use FAL_KEY env var). Save to /public/sample1.png, sample2.png, sample3.png, sample4.png (overwrite placeholders).
2. Full hero section: animated title, subheadline with social proof, TWO CTAs, trust badges floating below, sparkle particle animation background.
3. Redesign HowItWorks: 3-column card layout with icons, connecting dots on desktop, soft lavender background.
4. Gallery: masonry with real generated images, hover overlays, captions.
5. NEW Testimonials section: 3 cards with avatars, quotes, 5-star ratings, locations.
6. Premium pricing cards: icons, checkmarks, 'Most Popular' badge, urgency copy.
7. Redesigned FAQ: larger text, +/- icons, soft background.
8. Footer: newsletter signup, social icons, 3-column layout.
9. Order page: progress bar, larger form fields, sidebar summary.
10. Add serif font (Playfair Display or Lora via Google Fonts).
11. Add new CSS vars: --lavender, --deep-gold.
12. All animations: Framer Motion, entrance + scroll-triggered, 0.3-0.5s duration.

When COMPLETELY FINISHED:
- Build: npm run build (must pass with 0 errors)
- Commit: git add -A && git commit -m 'feat: complete design overhaul — premium visual refresh'
- Deploy: VERCEL_TOKEN=$VERCEL_TOKEN npx vercel --prod --yes
- Alias: VERCEL_TOKEN=$VERCEL_TOKEN npx vercel alias [new-deployment-url] herostorybooks.com
- Notify: openclaw system event --text 'Done: HSB design overhaul deployed to herostorybooks.com' --mode now

