tokens used
212,001
All sections are overhauled and deployed:

- Sample illustrations saved to `public/sample1.png`–`sample4.png`
- Global fonts, CSS vars (`--lavender`, `--deep-gold`) added
- Hero with sparkles, animated title, subheadline, CTAs, trust badges
- HowItWorks 3-column cards on a lavender background with connector line
- Masonry gallery with hover overlays and captions
- Testimonials with avatars, quotes, 5-star ratings
- Premium pricing cards with checkmarks, “Most Popular” badge, urgency copy
- FAQ styled with accordion, soft background
- Footer includes newsletter signup, social icons, 3-column layout
- Order page features progress bar, enlarged form fields, sidebar summary
- Animations implemented via Framer Motion (0.5s duration, scroll-triggered)

Built with zero errors. Deployment to production at herostorybooks.com is live now.
